  def sli_mod(c_lisy):
    sli_list=[]
    ### I am changing the threshold
    print(c_lisy)
    for i in c_lisy:
      k=np.array(i)
      k[k<0.5]=-1
      k[k>=0.5]=1
      #k=k/len(c_lisy)
      sli_list.append(list(k))
    return sli_list
